oints="0,852 1000,852 1000,994 0,994" /><Baseline points="0,992 1000,992" /><TextEquiv index="0"><Unicode>excusatione, et sine, in fine, combustione.</Unicode></TextEquiv></TextLine></TextRegion></Page></PcGts>